# ApiSources Module

## Overview

API Source Configuration supports multi-provider LLM management with auto-detection and model tiers

## Module Specs

| Type | Count | File |
|------|-------|------|
| Goals | 2 | [goals.ad](goals.ad) |
| Architecture | 2 | [architecture.ad](architecture.ad) |
